CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 5, 2014

[Cite as 03/05/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-797.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1807. In re Complaint of Toliver v. Vectren Energy Delivery of Ohio, Inc.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 12-3234-GA-CSS. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio.

Upon consideration of the motion for leave to intervene as appellee of Vectren Energy Delivery of Ohio, Inc., it is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
